    ITS - The right choice for any agency that promises better government
                           for the next century...
   Welcome!
      The Federal Technology Service's Office of Information Technology
      Solutions (ITS) is several complementary programs (listed @ left)
   tailored to e-Government executives needs. Check us out! Choose from a
    variety of value-added services @ various levels of support and cost.
   We support all types of IT projects and services through contracts with
               the private sector. The benefits of using ITS:
     * Quick response from Government technical and acquisition experts
     * Seasoned professionals in project and financial management
     * Fast, cost-effective access to the private sector
     * Excellent, innovative contracts
     * Nationwide and worldwide support


